    {
      "id": "PopularPost237452",
      "post_content": "In a sense, Nib is correct. The answer is on the card. Here's the answer in a less dickish manner:  \n  \nThe line in the reminder text that says and/or means that cards that are both birds and soldiers add only one. The \"and \" part means cards that are birds and soldiers and the \"or\" part means cards that are either birds or soldiers. Either way, you get 1 counter per card, never 2. So this would have 3 +1/+1 counters and be a 5/5.",
      "posted_by": "OpeeFomenom",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost237452\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">In a sense, Nib is correct. The answer is on the card. Here's the answer in a less dickish manner:<br/><br/>The line in the reminder text that says and/or means that cards that are both birds and soldiers add only one. The \"and \" part means cards that are birds and soldiers and the \"or\" part means cards that are either birds or soldiers. Either way, you get 1 counter per card, never 2. So this would have 3 +1/+1 counters and be a 5/5.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '237452'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42063\">OpeeFomenom</span>\r\n                                (4/12/2012 8:02:19 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSm